## Upgrading

```bash
helm upgrade db-query-operator \
  oci://ghcr.io/konnektr-io/charts/{{ template "chart.name" . }} \
  --namespace dbqo-system \
  --reuse-values
```

## Uninstalling

```bash
helm uninstall db-query-operator -n dbqo-system
```

**Note**: This does not delete the CRDs or managed resources.

